# Issues Encountered & Resolutions

| Issue | Resolution |
|-------|------------|
| `Send` import error | In LangGraph 1.x, `Send` is imported from `langgraph.types` instead of `langgraph.graph`. |
| `HttpUrl` serialization error | Replaced `HttpUrl` with `str` in `SourceSchema` and `ClaimSchema`. Converted Pydantic models to dictionaries via `.model_dump()`. |
| Parallel update conflict | Removed `current_agent` from the Extractor return because multiple parallel nodes should not update the same single-value field. |
| `SessionStatus` enum mismatch | Updated status values to match the enum definition (`running`, `completed`). |

